title: NHS R&D Lab: Bearings
description: The fourth installment of the NHS R&D Lab videos showcases the machinery used to test skateboard bearings; primarily the strength, speed, and durability. As always, the information gathered from both man and machine is used to evaluate the competition and our own Bearings innovations.
